## President's Report

<pre>
I was reminded earlier today that we've never completed and published our
annual report.  I don't immediately recall whether that stalled waiting for
further treasurer input, or is entirely my fault.  Regardless, I'm hoping to
resolve that before our next meeting.
</pre>


## Treasurer's Report

<pre>
